Every Thursday from 6pm to 11pm, Aperigiri celebrates the tradition of community, curating a selection of musicians and collectives who embody our passion for taste, style, and ethos.

Complementing this, our array of aperitif drinks and culinary offerings are designed to be simple yet profound, honorig the essence of refreshment.


For Tag Der Clubkultur 2024, Éclat Crew hosts a panel on maintaining a creative practice in a world of chaos. Éclat Crew DJs and visual artists round out the night. All welcome.
Éclat Crew is a Berlin-based Electronic Music Collective aiming to support, promote, and inspire the practice and output of FLINTA* artists of all levels through collaboration and cooperation.

Join us in this celebration.


// Donation-based (pay what you can)
// RSVP only
// Every Thursday from 18:00-23:00
// Aperitivo bites and drinks

/// TL;DR
3 collectives, 2 Floors, 1 Event. 
F1: Trance and Hard Trance. 
F2: Hard Groove and Hard Techno.

/// DESCRIPTION
TRINITY at M01 Club, Berlin, is a convergence of electronic exploration and communal harmony. Hosted by Cycling Club Collective, MWN KLLKTV, and Obstinsel Kollektiv, this event is a testament to the diverse and powerful spectrum of techno.

The first floor is dedicated to the raw, unfiltered energy of TRANCE and HARD TRANCE, while the second floor elevates the experience with a blend of HARD GROOVE and HARD TECHNO. Special guest DJs, celebrated for their unique styles and electrifying performances, will also grace our decks, adding to the night's dynamic soundscape.

/// TIMETABLE
TBA

/// TICKETING
TBA

/// GENERAL RULES
At TRINITY, we are committed to creating a safer and more inclusive space. We uphold a zero-tolerance policy towards any form of discrimination or harassment. This means no sexism, racism, classism, homophobia, xenophobia, or transphobia. We encourage kindness and respect. If you witness or experience anything contrary to these values, please inform our AWARENESS TEAM or any staff member. Inappropriate behavior will lead to an invitation to leave, and entry is at the club's discretion. Remember, no photos or videos, and no GBL/GHB!

Most importantly, SHARE THE LOVE!

/// LOCATION
M01
Markgrafendamm 1
10245 Berlin

